What is AMI?
Template used to launch EC2 instances.

Contains:

OS
Software
Configuration
Packages

Types:

AWS Managed AMI
Provided by AWS.

Marketplace AMI
Provided by vendors.

Custom AMI
Created by users.

Real-Time Scenario:
Need 100 Web Servers.

Without AMI:
Install Apache 100 Times

With AMI:
Install Once
Create AMI
Launch 100 Servers

Huge time savings.
